1
00:01:17,690 --> 00:01:18,992
Where have you been?

2
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:21,184
You didn't even show up for work this morning.

3
00:01:22,272 --> 00:01:24,270
Are you really not going to help me anymore?

4
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:32,408
I’m not staying here any longer.

5
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:37,104
And I’m done fighting for all of this.

6
00:01:43,376 --> 00:01:45,040
Are you stupid?

7
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:48,120
You were so close! Just a little more effort to discredit Pimchat

8
00:01:48,144 --> 00:01:49,712
and the presidency would have been yours.

9
00:01:49,896 --> 00:01:51,900
But did you ever even ask me...

10
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:54,744
if that’s what I wanted?

11
00:01:55,740 --> 00:01:59,664
Someone like you... if you aren’t the President, What else could you possibly be?

12
00:02:00,144 --> 00:02:02,140
What could someone like you ever supposed be, huh?

13
00:02:03,210 --> 00:02:04,896
Maybe I can't do it right now.

14
00:02:05,770 --> 00:02:08,080
But one day, I know I’ll be capable of something, Mom.

15
00:02:08,620 --> 00:02:09,328
Mom...

16
00:02:12,180 --> 00:02:13,792
don't you want to come and live with me?

17
00:02:15,488 --> 00:02:17,490
Let’s go back to living together, just the two of us,

18
00:02:19,060 --> 00:02:20,936
like we used to.

19
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:22,776
Are you crazy?

20
00:02:23,260 --> 00:02:24,448
Why on earth would I go back to that?

21
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:28,960
Don't you miss the times we spent together at all?

22
00:02:33,210 --> 00:02:36,096
If you’re not going to help me, then fine.

23
00:02:36,540 --> 00:02:40,912
But I’m going to stay right here

24
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:43,120
and haunt here until I get everything I deserve.

25
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:44,440
Mom!

26
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:50,240
Since I’ve already played the villain this much.

27
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:55,112
What does it matter if I destroy more people?

28
00:02:55,780 --> 00:02:57,536
If you’re going to be this weak,

29
00:02:57,860 --> 00:02:58,992
then just get out of my sight. Go!

30
00:03:19,770 --> 00:03:22,624
Ran, why haven't you been picking up?

31
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:25,520
Do you have any idea how chaotic today was?

32
00:03:25,568 --> 00:03:27,520
K’Chat was like a ticking time bomb,

33
00:03:28,860 --> 00:03:30,608
she was glaring at everyone all day.

34
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:34,384
I’m sorry...

35
00:03:36,232 --> 00:03:38,230
if it’s not too much to ask,

36
00:03:40,910 --> 00:03:44,304
Could you please take care of P'Chat for me?

37
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:47,080
Please tell P'Tina too.

38
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:53,872
I honestly have no idea what my mother is planning to do next.

39
00:03:58,250 --> 00:04:00,064
Why don't you come back and take care of her yourself?

40
00:04:00,104 --> 00:04:01,432
Why are you leaving her with me.

41
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,344
I can’t do that.

42
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:11,936
If I stay, I’ll just be used as a weapon to keep hurting her

43
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:15,160
over and over again.

44
00:04:19,420 --> 00:04:20,768
I can't stay here anymore.

45
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:28,496
But don't worry,

46
00:04:31,530 --> 00:04:36,072
everything is definitely going to end now.

47
00:04:51,620 --> 00:04:53,560
As I have informed everyone.

48
00:04:53,890 --> 00:04:57,960
Pimchat is simply not fit to continue leading this company.

49
00:05:01,296 --> 00:05:03,300
But I grew up with this company!

50
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:08,608
Or are you all going to argue

51
00:05:08,648 --> 00:05:12,360
that I haven’t worked tirelessly to make this business move forward?

52
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:17,624
Well, about that…

53
00:05:18,136 --> 00:05:20,140
But public image matters too, Khun Chat.

54
00:05:24,820 --> 00:05:28,472
You cannot prioritize image over my actual performance!

55
00:05:53,592 --> 00:05:54,496
What are you doing here?

56
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:03,824
I am here because there is a truth I must tell everyone.

57
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:20,512
K’Wichai’s death was not an accident.

58
00:06:32,060 --> 00:06:36,248
My mother was the one who planned the entire thing.

59
00:06:49,368 --> 00:06:52,024
What the hell are you talking about?!

60
00:06:55,140 --> 00:06:56,624
The evidence is in my hands now.

61
00:07:04,216 --> 00:07:04,792
Hey!

62
00:07:07,190 --> 00:07:08,768
What have you done?!

63
00:07:22,770 --> 00:07:26,480
Everyone, listen to me... I didn't do it. I’m not!

64
00:07:36,616 --> 00:07:37,816
How could you do this to me?

65
00:07:39,032 --> 00:07:42,472
Everyone, I didn't do it.

66
00:07:44,184 --> 00:07:46,752
How could you do this to me?

67
00:07:46,980 --> 00:07:48,472
How could you do this?!

68
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:51,720
It’s ruined! Everything is ruined!

69
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:53,152
Are you satisfied now?

70
00:07:53,184 --> 00:07:55,440
you ungrateful brat!

71
00:07:55,472 --> 00:07:56,920
How could you?!

72
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:59,256
She didn't do it alone.

73
00:08:08,424 --> 00:08:10,420
I was an accomplice to all of it.

74
00:08:13,392 --> 00:08:14,216
Ranya!

75
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:20,240
The two of us conspired together.

76
00:08:20,570 --> 00:08:21,320
Ranya, stop.

77
00:08:24,300 --> 00:08:25,680
You didn't do anything wrong.

78
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:28,912
If I’ve done anything wrong,

79
00:08:30,650 --> 00:08:32,512
it’s being born the daughter of a woman like this.
